{"tid":2038682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係屋企群組 公司群組Cap定圖 等班中國人冇得走佬","createTime":"2020-05-27T16:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T18:49:43.000Z","uid":45123,"like":173,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"89cc0ecfcbaeee0696ecef9d28f8bd2965cf6e60","tid":2038682,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"全球反中，收緊移民政策係可預見<br />\n<br />\n親中派，藍絲冇咁易離開香港，<br />\n<br />\n離開咗嘅，都可以比人掉番中國<br />\n既然佢地咁外國，緊喺要番祖家享受中國人榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以Cap定群組嘅圖，仲可以碌音 拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再係Send去佢地所移民嘅地方嘅移民部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n強制其國內有咁嘅移民，有咁大國家安全隱患<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n救得一個離鄉別井嘅中國人得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153aa1a48ae8765ab90753d0b68389c16c214f0c","tid":2038682,"uid":45123,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"拯救中國人計劃"},{"pid":"eacc116a25fac6dade5815e9175c740c6f550745","tid":2038682,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621206d8df60f6c428b66f1647dc7e3af32d53d0","tid":2038682,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fdec99e7978041ed0d82916c4acc9bd76ff5dc3","tid":2038682,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a8952d0d75b3c2f7440a366872af34918d9eb9","tid":2038682,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"